path.aria-label: "Via" and "Line to Shape" keepout areas need to be applied to positive & negative remote sense traces/nets
(i.e. VDD_xxx_HCPS_VOSNS/_GOSNS) both at the buck & along diff trace routing path between buckxOSNS pins
to ensure no unwanted power or Gnd connections are made before reaching the desired remote sense location
where only 1x power & Gnd connection should be made.
